net.varkhan.base.containers.queue
Interface IntQueue

All Superinterfaces:
Container<java.lang.Integer>, IntVisitable, java.lang.Iterable, Queue<java.lang.Integer>, Visitable<java.lang.Integer>
All Known Implementing Classes:
BoundedHeapIntQueue, OpenHeapIntQueue
public interface IntQueue
extends Queue<java.lang.Integer>, IntVisitable

A modifiable set of elements maintaining an internal order

A queue provides insertions, inspection and extraction operations on its elements, that follow the internal order, and may be subject to implementation-specific restrictions (bounds, delays, unicity...).
